dialogue.introduction: First ship of the Shiratsuyu-class destroyers, 'Shiratsuyu'!. Yes, the first ship!
dialogue.library_intro: Developed after the Hatsuharu-class destroyer, Shiratsuyu-class, number one, I'm Shiratsuyu! Yeah, number one, the first ship! With lots of upgrades, I'm a true fleet destroyer, you know! Eh? 'Don't be in such a rush that you'll hit a tanker'? Don't worry about it!
dialogue.secretary3: A~dmiral, do you want to talk to me that much? Alri~ght, I'll stay with you 'till the end!
dialogue.secretaryidle: Admiral ! work a little harder ! aim to be number one !
dialogue.secretarymarried: I want the Admiral to become everybody's number one~ Yeah! Today's a number one smile!
dialogue.wedding: *laugh* Admiral, what a nice feeling. My number one favourite thing? It's a se~cret!
dialogue.docking_complete: A ship has done repairing it seems.
dialogue.return_from_sortie: The operation's over, the fleet's come back, yeah?
dialogue.start_a_sortie: First ship of the Shiratsuyu class destroyers, Shiratsuyu, going out!
dialogue.night_battle: I'll be the first to continue the attack, bring it on!
dialogue.mvp: Of course I'm gonna be picked as number one! You know?
dialogue.moderately_damaged: ...It hurts, it's cold, it's embarrassing... Just you wait and see!
dialogue.new_year_2015: Happy New Year! Give me the most New Year's money! Admiral!
dialogue.setsubun_2015: Luck in, demons out! Heh heh, Setsubun might be fun! How do you feel about it, Murasame?
dialogue.valentines_day_2015: Admiral, here. I'll give you the tastiest one. Make sure you eat it, 'kay?
dialogue.white_day_2015: Admiral! Here! Give me the best return gift for Valentine's! Eh!? There isn't any~!?
dialogue.second_anniversary_2015: Admiral, it's the most important day today. We did it! I'm happy too! Yup!
dialogue.early_summer_2015: Dah~ And that was my favourite swimsuit... Unforgivable... Straight to the baths I go!
dialogue.midsummer_2015: Yeah, it's summer! Let's change our clothes and go to the beach! I'm going to be first one in!
dialogue.fall_2015: Hmm, so it's autumn. It's gotten a bit chilly, hasn't it? But it's still warm enough for short sleeves!
dialogue.fall_event_2015: The enemies are submarines, huh. No, if it is now I can also attack them! I practiced a lot, gained a lot of experience, equipment and skill are also the best! Probably... I can do it!
dialogue.christmas_2015: Merry Christmas! It's somehow fun! Christmas, its the best of the year!
dialogue.end_of_year_2015: Kyaa! This year also is going to end, all kinds of stuff to do, what to do first~!
